prompts.frontCover:
A humorous watercolor illustration featuring two cartoon characters based on the people in the reference photos, set against a soft, pale cream background with subtle paper texture. The younger character (Jordan) is playfully shown attempting to feed the older character (Lao Lao) a comically oversized dim sum dumpling with giant chopsticks. Lao Lao has a surprised and amused expression, with wide eyes and a laughing mouth, leaning back slightly. Both characters are rendered in a charming, illustrated style that highly resembles their reference photos, capturing their exact clothing (without logos), hairstyles, facial features, and body proportions. The scene is painted with soft, flowing watercolor washes, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds in warm, cheerful tones. In the center, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!".

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
